**Viewing Databases and Tables:**

•SHOW DATABASES:** Lists all existing databases.
19:54:42	SHOW DATABASES	7 row(s) returned	0.016 sec / 0.000 sec

•SHOW TABLES:** Lists all tables within the current database.
